title: Shades of Night 2
info:
composed by basehead of acid productions 5.20.94 - 6.30.94 (c)bh
ambient at its best? you decide.
samples: orb (cd), x-static goldmine (cd), moby.sanity, skaven.futurecrew, timelord, mantronix&tip.phenomena, sidewinder.megawatts
*sigh* alas... the long-(?)awaited sequel to the fairly well-distributed and well-accepted original S.O.N.
those familiar with it will notice a couple similarities. i worked quite alot on this one, something i usually don't do... i hope you enjoy it!
